CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 5, 1946, pg. 13, reads: "Hello There! Wishing you the best of everything in his own inimitable was is Lionel Lee Harris, youngest son of Mr. and Mrs. Charles (Teenie) Harris of Mulford Street. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of baby Lionel Lee Harris seated in toy vehicle, in home of Charles "Teenie" Harris, 7604 Mulford Street, Homewood
